{
  "stem": "21786.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the commando simply, who had something to do with getting the Jews out as quickly as possible, started.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was the yelling, there was the dogs, and then a kind of catastrophic noise, and out, out, out, and on the trucks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know how lucky we were at that point.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were taken to a camp in Auschwitz-Birkenau, B-I-R-K-E-N-A-U, Auschwitz zwei, 2, in something which was called the family camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Obviously, the Germans repeating the same story, trying to have something to show to the world.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I use the word Potemkin's village to show simply how, even in the most absurd circumstances, when they have got at least 200,000 or 250,000 Jewish workers working in the surrounding factories, which all began-- belonged to huge German companies, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that even there, they are being handled in certain kind of-- according to the Geneva Convention.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] There I started to form my basic rules of survival, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which helped, probably, many people, but which I had to break many times and kept me alive, so I don't know whether they are valid.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I was lecturing zillions of years after, so I had five rules of survival.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "First one was that you shall never be a hero.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You shall never volunteer to anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Third one, you shall be lucky.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The fourth one, you shall be really lucky.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In other words, you shall have 'mazel,' we are going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And number five, maybe, maybe, some of us are either lucky or they've got something that they will pick up a situation intuitively that they will do the right thing in the right moment at the right place.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "As I mentioned, I had to break the rule several times.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
